I made this 5 years ago as a tribute to Eric Garner, who kept saying “l can’t breathe “ as he was being choked to Death by NY cop Daniel Pantaleo for allegedly illegally selling cigarettes in the street. Today, attorney general William Barr has decided that Pantaleo won’t need to face federal civil rights charges for the death of Eric Garner #icantbreathe #police #nypd #policebrutality #ericgarner #blacklivesmatter #williambarr #attorneygeneral #policestate #animation #animatedgif #typography #politicalposter #danielpantaleo #racism #racistamerica #firepantaleo
